        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Perhaps now also can be better appreciated what the influence of such a study might and should be on practical action.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "At times economic students have gained the ear of statesmen and rulers, and have exercised much influence upon practical politics.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000006_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000006_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "It is sometimes bemoaned that economists have to day so small a direct part in the government of our republic.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "This test, however, is one that only astronomy can meet in any remarkable degree.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "There are countless unmeasured factors in human action.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Such generalizations as are possible must be based on actions that appear and reappear with practical constancy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Though a number of facts unite to suggest some conclusions as to the immediate future, the experience of the last century bids one beware of sweeping predictions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The optimists, with faith in the perfectability of human nature and of society, believed that all social ills were due to bad government; if despotism were but overthrown, man's nature would develop, untrammeled, to perfection.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The pessimists-the communists, and socialists of that day-seeing the same evils, had other explanations to offer.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "While the economists of that day believed the conditions of poverty and misery to be inevitable, the pessimists pronounced them unendurable, and advocated a radical social change as the only hope of saving the masses from starvation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000008_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000008_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "In such a variety of mutually contradictory views there must have been much error, but likewise much truth if it could be disentangled.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "It was not fully appreciated that a great change in social standards, controlling the growth of population, was in progress.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "This was the panorama of the progress of society as seen by both the conservative economists and the socialists of less than a century ago: continued invention, an increasing population, low wages, scanty food, growing wealth for the few, and growing poverty and misery for the masses.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Supply in the economic sense means the amount available at the given time in the market; but despite the great areas since brought into the world markets, the false idea of a century ago still persists in the text books, and shapes economic reasoning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "It is vain to say that the circumstances have been unique and that the general principle is still valid.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Much of the so-called orthodox economic analysis was essentially erroneous as applied to the conditions of the past century; it is erroneous to day and will be so for years to come, if it ever fits the facts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "New continents are about to be opened.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Population in Christendom has increased more rapidly than ever before in the history of the world, but it has not overtaken the progress in resources.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The rate of increase of population is slackening.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Despite the problems and the abuses that every new change brings, the civilized world undoubtedly is more prosperous to day than ever before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The greatest misery and discontent is in the more backward communities.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "This is past and present; what of the economic future?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Is the present condition a normal one-is this prosperity likely to grow or to decline?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000012_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000012_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Thus far, surely, the economic student may question the oracles; for though the distant future is veiled from man's view, the role of economic theory is to show causal relations, to convert mystery into reason, and thus to give a lamp to the feet of the present.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Living, he scratched the earth's surface, and dying, left his bones to fertilize the soil.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "But to day, man exhausts the stores in the interior of the earth, burns the treasures of the carboniferous age, casts the fertilizing elements into the ocean, and leaves the world an empty shell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Forests are being so rapidly cut off that the price of fuel wood and lumber in many parts of the United States has, within twenty years, been multiplied by three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The world's store of iron ore is not yet fully known, but much of it has been measured, and of the deposits known to be within the United States over one half are said to be owned by one corporation, and they are enough to continue its present output no more than sixty years.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Many other natural products are in like manner gathered by civilized man from a stock created long ago.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000015_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000015_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "While the supply of vegetable food promises to be ample, the supply of meat will be maintained with difficulty as population becomes denser.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The coal mines can be emptied, but so long as the sun shines and the rains fall, Niagara will remain as a source of light, heat, and power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The tides flow on forever.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "In every thunder storm enough force is dissipated to run thousands of factories.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The force in Mount Pelee, if chained and utilized, would run a million factories a million years.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Such a cheapening and diffusion of power would put a new face on many of the problems of industry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "It is reasonable to hope that before iron ore has become extremely scarce, a cheap and practicable method of extracting aluminium from clay will have been perfected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000018_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000018_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Secure of these permanent sources, civilization will stand on a firmer foundation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "When the coal districts are heaps of slag and cinders, industry will be found near the water power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Because of distance from raw materials, New England even now finds herself hard pushed in her rivalry with the Southern states in the manufacture of textiles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The industrial map of our country will be greatly altered a hundred years hence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "three.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "In order that a motive for saving may be present, there must be stable conditions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000022_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000022_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The difficult problems of the concentrated control of industry and of the control of wealth must be solved in the interests of all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Few thoughtful persons now hold the view that the race can be rapidly improved biologically by the process of educating the individual. Education is cumulative in so far as it builds up a better environment into which other children will be born, but the betterment is not due to the inheritance by the child of the acquired knowledge and skill of the parent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Practically, selection is the only means of improving the innate capacity of any species in any large measure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000026_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000026_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The weak, the ignorant, the incapable in primitive societies were ruthlessly killed off.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The strong, the sagacious, and the enterprising left the largest numbers of descendants.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "five.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Large families were the rule among the capable pioneers of America; now they are rare except in the lower industrial ranks. Democracy and opportunity are favoring this process of increasing the mediocre and reducing the excellent strains of stock.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "In a democracy, those of marked ability can more easily move into the better paid callings and professions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000028_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000028_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "That group of men, therefore, has left only three fourths enough descendants to maintain its numbers, and as the population has doubled within the same generation, that class represents only three eighths as large a proportion of the American stock as formerly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "If society were composed in equal parts of two distinct strains of stock, not intermarrying; if the total population kept intact from one generation to another (say each period of thirty years), but the superior strain contributed only three fourths of its own number, at the end of five generations it would have sunk from one half to a little more than one eighth of the population.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000030_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000030_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Progress is threatened unless social institutions can be so adjusted as to reverse the present process of multiplying the poorest, and of extinguishing the most capable families.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "six.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "In taking economic wants as the starting point of our study, it was not implied that men were entirely selfish.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Sympathy widens; economic wants include family, friends, and, in a growing measure, humanity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The happiness of a truly socialized man consists in part in the happiness of his fellows. As social sympathy broadens, the sense of duty becomes a stronger economic force.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Individual wants and interests must, so far as can now be seen, continue to be among the stronger forces that move society.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000032_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000032_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "Progress is made because to exceptional ability in general is now presented the hope of large rewards.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "These dynamic forces making for progress are at present, however, threatened from two sides.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The avoidance of certain kinds of work which, by social convention, come to be regarded as degrading, takes much ability out of business.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000035_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000035_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "The freedom of America to so great a degree from this disdain of honest labor has been a large factor in her progress, but it is endangered when men become timidly conservative of social position. Progress is threatened, secondly, by democracy, with its tendency to carry the notion of literal equality over into industry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000035_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000035_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "When democracy becomes envious, it denies to exceptional ability an exceptional reward. The line of growth must be the resultant of the positive forces in these two principles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7051_259009_000035_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7051/259009/7051_259009_000035_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7051",
        "content": "If this can be done, the economic outlook is for a great development of wealth and popular welfare.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]